CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 15, 2010

[Cite as 03/1512010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-946.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2009-1897. State ex rel. Turner v. Carthage Twp. Bd. of Trustees.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus. Upon consideration of relators’ application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
